WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  Find the pairs of numbers so that one number is the result
of the other, by following the type of operation (addition,
subtraction, multiplication or division) with the code number.
For example, if the type of operation is a multiplication and
the code number is 4, a pair of numbers to find would be 5
and 20.

  When you have found all the pairs of corresponding numbers,
the remaining number is the solution of the game.

  Have fun!

  As with all my Workbench games: the game window is resizeable
and the game board is redisplayed according to the new window
size.

